41,"uid":189430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:19:03.000Z","msg":"係咪回帶黎？"},{"pid":"39e3c1a4dc2087c055f78e1ee282751d0236a16a","tid":1222041,"uid":55854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:21:19.000Z","msg":"落地獄啦，賣港柒婆"},{"pid":"d82d46e73094b19eb9886049693f8f433760e341","tid":1222041,"uid":46356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:21:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪回帶黎？</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2015年11月1日星期日</span></span> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20151101/s00001/1446351419683/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20151101%2Fs00001%2F1446351419683%2F&d=Q%2BwKghBkVpQFldJLXg3PjcsFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=ea4c21b0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20151101%2Fs00001%2F1446351419683%2F&h=cf81c540\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20151101/s00001/1446351419683/</a><br />\n林鄭嘆政府工作堅持「正義」往往被責難：天堂已預位畀我 (12:13)"},{"pid":"6d7f7814c6b33a30fbd00de555ec83a8d12b1e1a","tid":1222041,"uid":13914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:23:55.000Z","msg":"Yes, 原本位預左俾你<br />\n<br />\n但你天堂有路你不走, 地獄無門闖進來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4effadfe52d2cb835978c5d02d6f44bd3cb17322","tid":1222041,"uid":107201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:33:00.000Z","msg":"第一誡：<br />\n除了我以外，你不可有別的神。（出埃及記20：3）<br />\n第二誡：<br />\n不可為自己雕刻偶像，也不可做甚麼形像彷彿上天、下地，和地底下、水中的百物。不可跪拜那些像，也不可事奉他，因為我耶和華─你的神是忌邪的神。恨我的，我必追討他的罪，自父及子，直到三四代；愛我、守我誡命的，我必向他們發慈愛，直到千代。（出埃及記20：4-6）<br />\n第三誡：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">不可妄稱耶和華─你神的名；因為妄稱耶和華名的，耶和華必不以他為無罪。（出埃及記20：7）</span><br />\n第四誡：<br />\n當記念安息日，守為聖日。六日要勞碌做你一切的工，但第七日是向耶和華─你神當守的安息日。這一日你和你的兒女、僕婢、牲畜，並你城裡寄居的客旅，無論何工都不可做；因為六日之內，耶和華造天、地、海，和其中的萬物，第七日便安息，所以耶和華賜福與安息日，定為聖日。（出埃及記20：8-11）<br />\n第五誡：<br />\n當孝敬父母，使你的日子在耶和華─你神所賜你的地上得以長久。（出埃及記20：12）<br />\n第六誡：<br />\n不可殺人。（出埃及記20：13）<br />\n第七誡：<br />\n不可姦淫。（出埃及記20：14）<br />\n第八誡：<br />\n不可偷盜。（出埃及記20：15）<br />\n第九誡：<br />\n不可作假見證陷害人。（出埃及記20：16）<br />\n第十誡：<br />\n不可貪戀人的房屋；也不可貪戀人的妻子、僕婢、牛驢，並他一切所有的。（出埃及記20：17）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCredit: <a href=\"https://www.testifygod.com/commandment.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.testifygod.com%2Fcommandment.html&d=Q%2BwKghBkVpQFldJLXg3PjcsFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=17e254d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.testifygod.com/commandment.html</a>"},{"pid":"0a5468ad06d5ad4a01f8ac0b1d6d055b76dc345f","tid":1222041,"uid":78612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:35:00.000Z","msg":"天堂無乜位啦，快啲上去啦，唔好浪費天父留比你既好嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢到有我地頂住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8ee799c87507cf7f5a1c53d7e8741d2324e4810","tid":1222041,"uid":8410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:35:11.000Z","msg":"林鄭係唔係思覺失調？ 你在位期間cut 老人福利cut醫療budget 喎"},{"pid":"06000a1e6886f03dd910e60b4341a10cebd85849","tid":1222041,"uid":229872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76d2068a3b37d88a7552ceee47a2b24826e5f6b9","tid":1222041,"uid":22558,"like":128,"dislike":1,"score":127,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T10:50:59.000Z","msg":"係喇係喇 得林鄭先睇得透係正義 香港人睇唔穿<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:37:34.000Z","msg":"1對100萬 對決，港人係佢地心中係咪就係蠢，100萬個腦都唔夠佢1個勁"},{"pid":"ed613924fdea4397f71fd499521dc17ae7d77f14","tid":1222041,"uid":54